'''Belfast''' ([[Anglikani ćhib|anglikanes]]: ''Belfast'', [[Irlandikani ćhib|irlandikanes]]: ''Béal Feirste'') si o sherutno foro vi o bareder foro le [[Nordutno Irland|Nordutne Irlandesko]], ando [[Phandlo Thagaripen]]. O [[Baro Belfast]] anderyarel vi forurya so truyaren les.

Lesko anav avel andar Béal Feirste, ''mui le Farsetosko'' (irlandikanes), sostar o foro kerdo pashal o than kai i len Farset chhorel pes ando [[Atlantikano Ocheano]].
